ensional-stdarray\/\">17.13 -- Multidimensional std::array<\/a>).\n<\/li>\n<li>Preprocessor directives <code>#elifdef<\/code> and <code>#elifndef<\/code> (no lesson yet).\n<\/li>\n<li>Preprocessor directive <code>#warning <\/code>(no lesson yet).\n<\/li>\n<li>Stacktrace library (no lesson yet)\n<\/li>\n<li>Standard library modules <code>std<\/code> (and <code>std.compat<\/code>) (no lesson yet).\n<\/li>\n<li>Static <code>operator()<\/code> and <code>operator[]<\/code> (no lesson yet).\n<\/li>\n<li><code>std::bitset<\/code> now fully constexpr.\n<\/li>\n<li><code>std::expected<\/code> (no lesson yet)\n<\/li>\n<li><code>std::ranges<\/code> algorithms <code>starts_with<\/code>, <code>ends_with<\/code>, <code>contains<\/code> (no lesson yet)\n<\/li>\n<li><code>std::string::contains<\/code> and <code>std::string_view::contains<\/code> (no lesson yet)\n<\/li>\n<li><code>std::to_underlying<\/code> to get the underlying type of enum (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.learncpp.com\/cpp-tutorial\/scoped-enumerations-enum-classes\/\">13.6 -- Scoped enumerations (enum classes)<\/a>).\n<\/li>\n<li><code>std::unreachable()<\/code> (no lesson yet).\n<\/li>\n<li>Using unknown pointers and references in constant expressions (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.learncpp.com\/cpp-tutorial\/stdarray-length-and-indexing\/\">17.2 -- std::array length and indexing<\/a>).\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"prevnext\"><div class=\"prevnext-inline\">\n\t<a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.learncpp.com\/cpp-tutorial\/appendix-c-the-end\/\">\n <div class=\"nav-button nav-button-next\">\n    <div class=\"nav-button-icon\"><i class=\"fa fa-chevron-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/div>\n    <div class=\"nav-button-text\">\n      <div class=\"nav-button-title\">Next lesson<\/div>\n      <div class=\"nav-button-lesson\">\n        <span class=\"nav-button-lesson-number\">C.1<\/span>The end?\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div><\/a>\n  \t<a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/\">\n  <div class=\"nav-button nav-butt